      <title>哈里斯计划下周在华盛顿与泽连斯基会面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/harris-plans-meeting-with-zelenskiy-in-washington-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，民主党候选人卡玛拉·哈里斯计划下周在华盛顿会见乌克兰总统泽连斯基，以拓宽她的外交政策形象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/harris-plans-meeting-with-zelenskiy-in-washington-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 00:43:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将访问斯普林菲尔德，回应毫无根据的宠物食用指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/trump-to-visit-springfield-town-at-center-of-pet-eating-claims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普表示，他计划访问两个城镇，这两个城镇已成为全国移民辩论的焦点，也是前总统宣扬的有关移民的毫无根据的阴谋论的中心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/trump-to-visit-springfield-town-at-center-of-pet-eating-claims</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 00:33:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国对美游说策略失败，科技公司面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/china-s-failing-us-lobby-playbook-puts-tech-companies-at-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国议员向中国发出信号，无论11月大选后谁控制华盛顿，世界第二大经济体及其企业在可预见的未来都将在美国面临严峻挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/china-s-failing-us-lobby-playbook-puts-tech-companies-at-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本男学生在中国遭刺伤后死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/japanese-boy-stabbed-in-china-dies-nhk-says-m18ie81i</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名 10 岁日本儿童在中国南方被刺伤，目前已死亡，这一事态发展可能进一步加剧两国关系紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/japanese-boy-stabbed-in-china-dies-nhk-says-m18ie81i</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 23:43:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本或将击败美国，任命首位女性领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/japan-may-beat-the-us-to-install-its-first-female-leader</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在本月举行的首相选举中，日本有一位女性候选人位列前茅，这使得这个以缺乏多样性而闻名的国家可能先于美国任命其首位女性领导人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/japan-may-beat-the-us-to-install-its-first-female-leader</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 23:15:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国的镇压正在粉碎一代人的梦想</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/xi-risks-economy-as-china-crushes-dreams-mental-health-of-a-generation-podcast</link>
      <description><![CDATA[ 在今天的 Big Take Asia 播客中，中国重大政策转变如何颠覆了数百万专业人士的生活、减少了工作岗位、削减了工资并粉碎了梦想。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/xi-risks-economy-as-china-crushes-dreams-mental-health-of-a-generation-podcast</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 23:09:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>研究发现公众高估了英国寻求庇护者的数量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/public-overestimates-asylum-seeker-numbers-in-uk-study-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智库研究发现，英国公众严重高估了以庇护寻求者身份来到英国的移民数量，这种误解扭曲了有关移民政策的讨论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-18/public-overestimates-asylum-seeker-numbers-in-uk-study-finds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Sep 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
